{"lastModified":1771253253188,"uri":"c::17951852342::vessel::c05133f0-37b9-11f0-b94c-2377f1d0765f","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nIntroducing Solon, a stylish 4-cabin sailing yacht, the Beneteau Oceanis 46.1, fresh off the dock in 2022 and now calling Marina Alimos, Greece home.\n\nSolon comfortably hosts up to 10 guests in its four cozy double cabins and roomy saloon, offering two extra beds for added relaxation. Pillows and blankets are thrown in for that extra touch of comfort.\n\nWith four toilets and a shower, convenience and comfort are always close at hand onboard Solon.\n\nEquipped with a rolling mainsail, solar panels, generator, bimini, and bow thruster, Solon promises both efficiency and reliability on the water. Stay cozy with heating and air conditioning, while the audio system, inside and outside speakers, set the mood for your sailing experience.\n\nWhip up your favorite meals in the fully-equipped galley, complete with an oven, cooker, sink, and kitchen utensils, ensuring every meal is a treat.\n\nEmbark on an unforgettable sailing journey aboard Solon, where luxury, convenience, and relaxation await against the breathtaking backdrop of the Greek coastline.","blueprint":{"name":"SOLON","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::c05133f0-37b9-11f0-b94c-2377f1d0765f::assets::967f4610-37bf-11f0-881f-9fee4797d48f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c05133f0-37b9-11f0-b94c-2377f1d0765f::assets::9656d680-37bf-11f0-881f-9fee4797d48f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c05133f0-37b9-11f0-b94c-2377f1d0765f::assets::96893120-37bf-11f0-881f-9fee4797d48f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c05133f0-37b9-11f0-b94c-2377f1d0765f::assets::96890a10-37bf-11f0-881f-9fee4797d48f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c05133f0-37b9-11f0-b94c-2377f1d0765f::assets::967dbf70-37bf-11f0-881f-9fee4797d48f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c05133f0-37b9-11f0-b94c-2377f1d0765f::asse